1404
01:42:23.828 --> 01:42:25.955
<i>Langere passen,
pomp met je armen.</i>


1405
01:42:26.038 --> 01:42:29.125
Knokken, Hannah.
-Pak haar, Hannah.


1406
01:42:29.208 --> 01:42:31.377
Knokken.
-Zo, ja.


1407
01:42:31.460 --> 01:42:33.588
Hup, Hannah.
-Knokken, kom op.


1408
01:42:33.671 --> 01:42:36.424
<i>Hou je ogen op de finish
en knok ervoor.</i>


1409
01:42:36.507 --> 01:42:39.051
<i>Ik ben bij je. 
Je kunt dit.</i>

1410
01:42:39.135 --> 01:42:40.553
Ik kan je zien winnen.

1411
01:42:40.636 --> 01:42:42.305
<i>Ik kan je zien winnen.</i>

1412
01:42:42.388 --> 01:42:44.515
<i>Doe het. Doe het, dochter.</i>

1413
01:42:44.599 --> 01:42:47.101
<i>Doe het, Hannah.</i>
-Gina. Rennen.

